INSERT INTO [dbo].[Content] ([ColumnUuid], [IsDeleted], [ID], [ColumnTitleText], [ColumnTitle], [ColumnNum], [AddTime], [AddPeople], [SuperiorUuid], [SuperiorMenu], [ColumnType], [ColumnModel], [ColumnUrl], [ColumnPic], [Staue], [ColumnWord], [ColumnContent], [ColumnVideo], [ColumnAudio], [ColumnFile], [SortID], [IssueTime], [IsStick]) VALUES (N'43059794-6E18-4394-8550-7A8D48B7D0F9', N'0', N'21', N'实验进程', N'化学实验教学中心实验室开放管理制度', NULL, N'2011-02-23 11:28:39.000', N'admin', N'626386FF-F75E-4966-A7E8-F017E895B0BB', N'2', NULL, N'列表栏目', N'upload/Zhongxin/201102231522502264.pdf', NULL, N'1', NULL, N'<p style="text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><font size="2"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（二</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">OO</font></span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二年十月修订）</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoBodyTextIndent"><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;" lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="2">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoBodyTextIndent"><font size="2"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">化学实验开放运行有利于培养学生的实践能力和创新精神，是当前人才培养模式改革的重点之一。为使该项工作顺利进行，特制定本制度。</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoBodyTextIndent"><font size="2"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一、实验室开放的具体做法：</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; tab-stops: list 0cm" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">化学实验教学中心建设成为省级化学实验教学示范中心后，努力对学生实行全天候开放，至少要有每天</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">14</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">小时的开放时间，并试行学生自己选时和选课制。</span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 26.25pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; tab-stops: list 0cm" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="2">具体做法：</font></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="2">①实验室开放时间安排：实验时间分上午、下午、晚上三个单位时间；</font></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="2">②实验项目公布：实验室定时书面或在校园网上公布具体的实验安排，分必修与选修，以班级为单位，在实验开始前两周预约或在校园网上预约；</font></span></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">③校内外开放：<span style="color: black">现阶段主要对我校化工学院、生物与环境工程学院、药学院、建工学院等学院相关专业的学生开放，承担函授、夜大、脱产班等成教学生及民办学院学生的化学实验教学任务，逐步扩大对省内其它学校相关专业的开放。</span></span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二、实验成绩考核：</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">实验成绩考核：考试实验成绩占</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">40%</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。平时实验成绩占</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">60%</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三、教学方式：</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">学生按照预约时间进入实验室，提交预习报告，独立做实验。指导教师实行值班制，每个实验室每次实验安排一名教师和一名实验技术人员。教师要树立学生在实验过程中的主体地位，不独占整个教学活动时间，但是要发挥主导作用，对实验内容要认真研究，将实验中的基本技术训练、基本技能训练、综合实验能力和创新思维能力训练等，针对不同需要确定教师应采取的不同指导方法。基本技术实验，教师要做规范演示操作，对学生严格要求；基本技能训练，教师只进行重点讲解，要求学生仔细阅读仪器设备说明书，并在动手过程中及时纠正错误；综合实验能力训练重点培养学生的实验设计能力、观察能力、数据处理、分析能力等，要求学生拟出实验方案、实验步骤，学生自主完成。</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">四、实验室管理模式：</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、日常教学实验，实行值班教师负责制。</span><span style="color: black" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoBodyTextIndent"><font size="2"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、研究生实验、本科生毕业论文，实行指导教师负责制。需借用实验室仪器设备，首先要保证本科生日常实验教学的需要，由指导教师书面填写借条，实验室登记，按时归还。归还时，要保证仪器设备的性能良好，如有损坏、遗失，按价赔偿。</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-indent: 10.5pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0" class="MsoBodyTextIndent"><font size="2"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>3</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、教师科研工作需借用实验室仪器设备，同样首先要保证本科生日常实验教学的需要，书面填写借条，实验室登记，按时归还。归还时，要保证仪器设备的性能良好，如有损坏、遗失，按价赔偿。</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、外校实验，应事先联系，征得实验室同意，根据学校、学院规定签定协议。</span></font></p>
<p style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; tab-stops: 44.25pt" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">化学实验教学中心开放实验室登记表</span><span style="font-size: 15pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 黑体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></strong></p>
