<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、为了保证实验教学的顺利进行，实验室的仪器设备必须处于良好的工作状态。指定专职人员负责仪器设备领用、验收、维护保养、联系维修事务，由实验室主任监督执行。全体人员必须自觉关心、参与和配合这项重要工作。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验室主任必须在学校职能部门规定的时间内，制订出仪器设备的申购计划、报废计划，添置补充新仪器，以满足实验教学的需要。制定计划时，必须充分考虑使用率的问题，避免闲置浪费。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、仪器的使用者，严格按照仪器使用规则操作，严禁擅自改变仪器操作要点，仪器存放位置，如确需改变者，应经管理人员同意，使用后应及时恢复原状。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、使用各类仪器，应如实填写仪器设备使用记录。违规操作而导致仪器损坏者，应及时报告实验室主任，按实验室有关条例处理。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、仪器设备每年核对一次，做到帐、物、卡相符，一旦发现问题，应通报理学院和学校有关部门，以便及时处理。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'0', N'2011-02-23 15:41:04.067', N'0')
GO

INSERT INTO [dbo].[Content] ([ColumnUuid], [IsDeleted], [ID], [ColumnTitleText], [ColumnTitle], [ColumnNum], [AddTime], [AddPeople], [SuperiorUuid], [SuperiorMenu], [ColumnType], [ColumnModel], [ColumnUrl], [ColumnPic], [Staue], [ColumnWord], [ColumnContent], [ColumnVideo], [ColumnAudio], [ColumnFile], [SortID], [IssueTime], [IsStick]) VALUES (N'A38887D9-93DB-4A8B-A507-0BE09EF3F517', N'0', N'25', N'实验进程', N'化学实验教学中心低值易耗品、耐用品的管理办法', NULL, N'2011-02-23 15:43:30.363', N'admin', N'626386FF-F75E-4966-A7E8-F017E895B0BB', N'2', NULL, N'列表栏目', N'upload/Zhongxin/201102231543283226.pdf', NULL, N'1', NULL, N'<p style="text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><font size="2"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(2003 </font></span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">5 </font></span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月修订</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)<o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">低值</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">耐用品</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">指凡不符合固定资产标准，不属材料范围但可长期使用又不易损坏的物资，如仪表、工具、量具和一般器皿等；易耗品指玻璃器皿、电子器件、配件和劳动保护用品等，不属于材料且在使用过程中容易损坏的物资。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、采购计划由各实验室根据仓库库存量，汇总各门实验课的低值易耗品申购计划，报实验中心审批后，按有关规定统一采购，保证实验顺利开出。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、各实验室建立低值易耗品帐本，帐本上要记有物品的名称、规格、单价、数量、入库时间、出库时间及数量等。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、低值</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">耐用品由各实验室申报计划，报中心主任审批，中心资产员做好</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">低值</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">耐用品帐本。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">低值</span><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">耐用品的报废按学校有关规定执行。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验室仓库物品只供应实验教学使用，由实验室主任并履行出库登记手续。科研课题所需物品由课题负责人自行采购或委托实验室采购，或经实验室主任批准后借用，并尽快偿还。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、仓库库存物品要定位、分类、有序存放，帐物对号。易燃、易爆、有毒物品等按本实验室专门条例管理。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">6</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、领用出库的物品由实验室主任指定的专职人员负责使用或保管。要注意节约，不得带出实验室。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、本办法由实验室主任、中心资产员监督执行。</span></font></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'0', N'2011-02-23 15:43:30.363', N'0')
GO

INSERT INTO [dbo].[Content] ([ColumnUuid], [IsDeleted], [ID], [ColumnTitleText], [ColumnTitle], [ColumnNum], [AddTime], [AddPeople], [SuperiorUuid], [SuperiorMenu], [ColumnType], [ColumnModel], [ColumnUrl], [ColumnPic], [Staue], [ColumnWord], [ColumnContent], [ColumnVideo], [ColumnAudio], [ColumnFile], [SortID], [IssueTime], [IsStick]) VALUES (N'355F0BB6-7EC3-4C74-BFAC-1BD6E78BEC90', N'0', N'26', N'实验进程', N'化学实验教学中心安全“四防”措施', NULL, N'2011-02-23 15:44:39.363', N'admin', N'626386FF-F75E-4966-A7E8-F017E895B0BB', N'2', NULL, N'列表栏目', N'upload/Zhongxin/201102231544035816.pdf', NULL, N'1', NULL, N'<p style="text-align: center; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><st1:chsdate w:st="on" year="2003" month="5" day="24" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False"><font face="Times New Roman">2003 </font><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''" lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">年</span></span><font face="Times New Roman">5 </font><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''" lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">月</span></span><font face="Times New Roman">2</font></st1:chsdate><font face="Times New Roman">4 </font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">日</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">修订</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">)<o:p></o:p></font></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="2" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验室与办公室分开，室内及走廊不得存放自行车及生活用品。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验室大门每次下班时都要锁好。无关人员不得进入实验室。实验大楼有专人值班，值班人员负责整栋大楼的安全卫生工作，下班时锁大楼总门。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验室钥匙不得自行复制，钥匙持有者应对实验室的安全负责，丢失钥匙应及时声明，并及时换锁。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验室内严禁吸烟、饮食。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验室内的进水管道、下水道要保持通畅，不好用的水龙头应及时换掉，电路应保持完好，无老化、短路现象，及时消除隐患。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">6</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验药品、仪器分类保存，易燃易爆药品与其他药品分开存放。仪器、药品一般不外借。未用完的原装药品要及时收藏保存。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">7</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、实验过程中，要严格按实验指导书的要求进行操作，特别是对易燃易爆有毒药品的使用应谨慎小心。残渣废液应及时处理。药品、仪器任何人都不得擅自带出实验室。实验结束时，实验指导教师必须与实验人员核对有关物品后，方可离开实验室。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">8</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、每个实验室都要配备消防器材和细砂。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">9</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、节假日之前要进行安全检查。切断电源，关好水龙头、关窗、锁门、贴封条。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><font size="2"><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、如有违反上述规定而发生事故者，应追究当事人和有关人员的责任，并严肃处理。</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
<p style="text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">本措施自</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2003 </font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">年</span><span style="mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">5 </font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">月实行，以前的相关措施如与本措施有冲突，按此措施执行。</span></font></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, N'0', N'2011-02-23 15:44:39.363', N'0')
