oman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">，</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW" lang="ZH-TW">应办理有关登记手续</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">，</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW" lang="ZH-TW">说明用途。</span><span style="line-height: 140%; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt" lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>
